Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.61,0:01:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{作戦なき作戦}—Episode 013—\NStrategy without strategy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.71,0:01:56.63,Sign,,0,0,0,,{全国中学女子バレーボール選手権大会}All-Japan Middle School Girls Volleyball Championships
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.28,0:01:50.34,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{全国中学バレー選手権大会もこのXXXで、}In the All-Japan Volleyball Championships…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.34,0:01:53.14,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{参加チーム三十二このうち、八こが残り。}…out of 32 participant teams only 8 are still in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.14,0:01:55.56,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{いよいよ、優勝を争うことに成りましたが。}The quarter finals are finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.56,0:01:57.56,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{さて、どこが本命なのか？}Who will emerge victorious?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.56,0:02:00.35,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{スポーツ評論家の山口さんに聞いてみたいと思います。}Let's ask a\hsports\hcommentator, Yamaguchi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.35,0:02:01.34,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{どうでしょう、山口さん？}How is it, Yamaguchi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.34,0:02:03.29,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{本命と言うことになりますと？}What teams do you think are likely to win?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.29,0:02:04.08,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{あぁ、}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:07.65,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{や、今年はXXXは続きましてね。}Well, things seem to have taken a weird turn this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.65,0:02:11.05,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{優勝候補に(XXXあがった)ベストエイトXX残ったのは…}Unprecedentedly, out of the eight teams that made it here…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.72,0:02:14.44,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{明法学園、奥山中学二号だけで、}…except Meihou Academy and Okuyama Middle School…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:16.86,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{あとの六は全部東京大会。始めてですね。}…the other six schools all come from outside Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.50,0:02:19.03,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{大したもんですね。}It's not easy to pick someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.03,0:02:21.18,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{得に優勝候補再入力の…}Especially considering how the favorite…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.18,0:02:23.78,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{(XXX・もう岩井中を予選で破っていない)。}…Iwai Middle School has lost in the qualifiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.78,0:02:28.37,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{ワンセットの落としていない、福岡中の全く底知れない力がXますな。}Fukuoka Middle School, who hasn't lost a single set yet, seems very powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.94,0:02:31.57,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{さて、初出場の富士見学園はどうでしょうか？}What about the debuting team, Fujimi Academy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.90,0:02:36.16,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{そう。このチームは美少女アタックコンビとして、今大会評判のようです。}Yeah. They are famous for their beautiful attack duo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.16,0:02:38.19,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{実力もそうとXXね。}I wonder about their overall skill though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.19,0:02:39.90,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{明法といい勝負でしょう。}Meihou is bound to give us a fine game.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:41.48,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{でも、面白いのは福岡中です。}However, Fukuoka is a curious case.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.04,0:02:44.31,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{かきのうちはワンマンチームですが、}Kakinouchi might be a one man team, however…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.31,0:02:47.59,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{彼女の回転レシーブ以外どうと言うこともないチームなのに。}…except for her revolving receive, their team has nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.59,0:02:50.08,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{(XXX・不思議)と相手の方から負けて言ってもですね。}They're pretty mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:50.65,Blackboard,,0,0,0,,{福岡中学}Fukuoka Middle School
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.08,0:02:52.64,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{ずばり言って、どうでしょうか？}What's the final decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.18,0:02:56.19,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{ま、今言った—明法、福岡、富士見だ。}Right now I'd say Meihou, Fukuoka, Fujimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.19,0:02:58.56,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{この三戸の優勝を争うと言っていいでしょう。}I'd place these three in that order.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:01.72,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:02.89,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.43,0:03:05.87,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{いいぞ、アタックコンビ！}Nice, attack duo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.00,0:03:07.42,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,{頑張ってね！富士見！}Good luck, Fujimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.11,0:03:07.42,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{頑張れよ！}Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.55,0:03:08.67,Blackboard,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2150,0)}{四国中・富士見中}Shikoku ・ Fujimi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.98,0:03:09.44,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.63,0:03:09.98,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.98,0:03:10.44,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:11.26,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.26,0:03:11.91,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:12.92,Blackboard,,0,0,0,,{四国中・富士見中}Shikoku ・ Fujimi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.55,0:03:15.26,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん、マッチポイントよ。}Ayuhara-san, it's a match point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:16.85,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{この試合をストレートいただきね。}We've got this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.23,0:03:17.76,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{うん。}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:20.40,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{でも問題は次のこのコートでやる福岡中よ。}But the problem is Fukuoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:22.31,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{サーブを得意投げてね。}Give us a good serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:23.76,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{任しておいて。}Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:26.04,Alternative,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{行くわよ。}Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:32.96,Alternative,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{伝家の宝刀。}Special technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:33.81,Alternative,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{「木の葉落とし」。}"Leaf Fall".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.57,0:03:35.57,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.57,0:03:35.91,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.83,0:03:42.25,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{よかった。}I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.19,0:03:47.44,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{今日も勝った。}Today we won as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:48.86,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{明日は準決勝。}Tomorrow is the semi-final.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.86,0:03:50.06,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{そして決勝！}Then, the final!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.76,0:03:52.37,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{でも気になるは、福岡中。}But I'm worried about Fukuoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.89,0:03:55.34,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{(XXX・なんか痛いの知り合い不気味な)存在。}I feel as if they're hiding some special weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:03:56.84,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{見たい。}I want to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.43,0:04:00.09,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{福岡中の試合を見たい。}I want to see Fukuoka's game!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.46,0:04:05.22,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{先生、今日これから福岡中の試合を見るんでしょう？}Professor, we're going to stay and see Fukuoka's games, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:09.00,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{実勢を見てX作戦を立てようがない。}We can't form a strategy without seeing the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.00,0:04:10.10,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{そうですね、先生？}Am I right, professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:10.45,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{ん？}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.83,0:04:13.36,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{いや、見ることはない。}Nah. There's no need to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.36,0:04:14.63,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{皆、宿に帰る。}Let's go back to the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:15.98,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,{そ—そんな!}I-It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:17.29,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,{先生、見せてください。}Professor, let us stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:20.99,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,{新聞やテレビの色んな報道聞いてると不安に成ってくるんです。}I'm worried about various press reports in the newspapers and on the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:23.97,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{先生。研究して作戦を立てるとしたら、}Professor, if we're to form a strategy…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.97,0:04:25.76,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{今日次の試合見るしかないんです。}…we have to stay and see their game.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.76,0:04:26.93,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{是非見せてください。}Please let us stay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.93,0:04:27.83,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{見なくていい。}There's no need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:28.37,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:29.37,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{どうしてですか？}But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:31.05,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{あたしには先生が分かりません。}I don't understand, professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:34.20,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{だって、明日明法が負けたら、嫌んでも福岡中と当たります。}After all, if Meihou loses tomorrow, we'll be facing Fukuoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.16,0:04:35.93,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{分かってる。}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.36,0:04:37.55,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{所で、君たちは…}By the way…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:41.11,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{札幌とか明法には勝てても、福岡中とでは勝自身がない。}…unlike Sapporo and Meihou,\Nyou don't think you can win with Fukuoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:42.01,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{そうなのか？}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:44.17,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{鮎原、君はどうだ？}Ayuhara, how is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.53,0:04:45.89,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あ、そんなことありません。}That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:47.05,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{よし。早川はどうだ？}Good. Hayakawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:48.94,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{絶対自信があります。}I absolutely believe in us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.94,0:04:49.94,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{絶対?}Absolutely?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.94,0:04:50.82,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{ま、いいだろう。}Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.82,0:04:52.03,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{皆はどうなんだ？}What about the rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.03,0:04:54.31,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,{キャプテンや早川さんに同じです。}We feel the same as captain and Hayakawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:56.80,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{要するに、全員勝自身があると言うわけだな？}So you're saying you all believe in yourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:04:57.89,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{—はい！\N—はい！}– Yes sir!\N– Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.89,0:04:58.48,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{よし。}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:04:59.63,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{それならいい。}That's good then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.63,0:05:01.44,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{わざわざ試合なず見ることはない。}There's no point in watching them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:04.73,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{君たちはその自信あれば、福岡中など恐れるX。}With your confidence, there's nothing to fear about Fukuoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:06.02,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{さ、引き上げるんだ。}We're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.02,0:05:07.29,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{そんな、先生！}B-But, professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.29,0:05:08.45,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{さ、Xたくするんな。}Come on already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:13.16,Sign,,0,0,0,,{旅館やまと}Hotel "Yamato"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.09,0:05:19.56,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{鮎原や早川達が…}Ayuhara, Hayakawa and the girls…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:21.19,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{…今動揺してるのはよく分かる。}…are disturbed. I understand them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.16,0:05:25.42,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{しかし、それは自信がないと言うとようとは根本的に違う。}But it's not the same as having no confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.90,0:05:30.08,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{今、富士見が福岡中に勝つためには…}What Fujimi needs to win right now is…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:32.02,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{…絶対勝てるという自信を持つことだ。}…an absolute belief that they can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.05,0:05:35.38,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{マイペースを崩しては成らんのだ。}We need to do it at our pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:40.03,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{福岡中の、あのわけの分からない勝ち方を皆に見せたら…}If I showed them the Fukuoka's tactic now…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:45.03,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{…相手をバカにしてしまって有段をするか。}…they'd be no longer serious and let their guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:49.03,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{どう戦っても、とても勝てないと絶望してしまうかも。どちらかになってしまう。}Then again I can't have them think they can't win no matter what they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:52.70,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{それでは、勝利の道は開かれない。}The path to victory will close this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:54.15,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{勝つためには…}In order to win…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.15,0:05:56.17,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{…作戦なき作戦。}…we need a strategy without strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.17,0:05:57.37,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{これしかない。}That's our only choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:58.33,Blackboard,,0,0,0,,{第一試合：富士見学園対札幌中}First match: Fujimi vs. Sapporo
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.07,0:06:00.45,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,{頑張れよ！}Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.26,0:06:03.29,Blackboard,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,120,120,0,1250,0,0)}{札幌中・富士見中}Sapporo ・ Fujimi
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.37,0:06:05.00,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.00,0:06:05.39,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:06.34,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.87,0:06:12.87,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{今日までXXX合解なXXX勝ち進んでまいりました、北海道もの札幌中が…}Having emerged from the qualifiers with no major mistakes, Sapporo Middle School from Hokkaidou…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:18.50,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{…富士見中の美少女アタックコンビの変幻自在の攻撃の前に…}…has evident trouble with defending against the Fujimi Academy's beautiful attack duo. {…しっかり直りXXXあります。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:19.88,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:20.86,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:22.22,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,{いいぞ、いいぞ！}Good, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:27.81,Blackboard,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1350,1350)}{札幌中・富士見中}Sapporo ・ Fujimi
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.50,0:06:31.08,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:32.66,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.05,0:06:41.87,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{全く調子の上がっている、富士見学園であります。}Fujimi achieves a crushing victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.87,0:06:45.07,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{これは福岡中の全勝についで優秀な成績であります。}It is an excellent outcome after all the Fukuoka's victories.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.52,0:06:47.34,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,{いいぞ！}Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.67,0:06:55.14,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{は、福岡中。}Ah, it's the Fukuoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:04.03,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{福岡中ね。}Hey, it's the Fukuoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:06.21,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{あたしたちの試合をずっと見ていたのね。}They were watching us all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:08.59,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{試合前だって言うのに。}Even before the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:12.84,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あのかきのうちよしこの目が試合中あたしの体にXXと思うと…}I felt Kakinouchi Yoshiko's eyes on me during the entire match.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:14.44,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あ、なんだか気味が悪いわ。}It feels creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:17.23,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{そうね。嫌らしい目つきあたしたちを。}Yeah. She had such a dirty look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:19.71,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{そうか。あたしたちを研究しに来てたのね。}They must've come to research our game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:21.22,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{きっと今までも何度か。}It probably was for the nth time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:23.84,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{何度か来ていたのは知っている。}I know it must've been several times.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.82,0:07:27.32,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{今しみつくされてしまった感じがするわ。}I feel frozen right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.85,0:07:29.93,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あたしたちも福岡中の試合を見たり…}We also should watch their game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:30.47,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{おい。}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.87,0:07:31.83,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{鮎原に早川。}Ayuhara. Hayakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:34.37,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{—控室へ戻るぞ。\N—せ—先生！}– We're going to the waiting room.\N– P-Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:34.91,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{何だ？}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:37.37,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{次の試合をあたしたちに見せてください。}Please let us stay for the next game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:38.73,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{ん？未だ始まったな。}Eh? Here we go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.98,0:07:39.80,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{そうです。}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.80,0:07:43.06,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{今福岡中の人達が試合をずっと見ていたんです。}The Fukuoka's team saw our entire game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.36,0:07:44.14,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:46.73,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{知ってるよ。}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.06,0:07:48.35,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{じゃ、見ていいんですね。}Then it's okay to watch, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.35,0:07:49.05,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{ちょっと待て。}Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:51.14,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{君たちは…}You girls…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.14,0:07:53.25,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{…相手の試合を見たい見たいと言うんだが…}…keep pleading "let us stay, let us stay", but…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.25,0:07:54.82,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{…どうしてそんなに見たいんだ？}…why do you want to see it so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:07:56.80,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{もう何度も言いました。}We've explained it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.14,0:07:58.78,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{そうです。相手を知ることX。}It's to research our opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.78,0:08:00.94,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{君たちは相手をよく知ってるはずだ。}You know your opponents plenty already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.94,0:08:02.86,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{メモ。泉のメモを読んだじゃないか？}Haven't you read Izumi's memo earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.38,0:08:04.89,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{そうじゃない、先生。}That's not enough, professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.89,0:08:07.29,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{確かにあのメモからは色々分かりました。}Indeed, we've learned a lot from that memo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:10.45,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{でも、実際に試合でどう活かしてるのか見たいだけです。}But it can't replace seeing the opponent in a real match.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:12.50,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{可笑しいじゃないか。}That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:14.90,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{なぜそう福岡中だけ拘る？}Why are you so worried about Fukuoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:15.86,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.86,0:08:18.13,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{明法は決勝の相手になるかもしれないんだぞ。}You might be playing the finals with Meihou.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.96,0:08:21.06,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{明法の場合はあたしがよく知ってます。}I know Meihou very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:22.71,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{どんなさ苦戦だって。}I can come up with a strategy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:26.11,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{いつ鮎原にコーチに成ったんだ？}Ayuhara, when did you become a coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:28.43,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{私に代わって作戦を立てるつもりか？}Are you planning to form a strategy in my stead?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.43,0:08:29.20,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.20,0:08:30.17,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{XX、そんな…}Th-That's not it…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.63,0:08:31.93,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{それじゃ、私に任してX。}Then leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:33.52,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{さ。控室へ行こう。}We're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.68,0:08:39.99,Blackboard,,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,1200)}{明法中・福岡中}Meihou ・ Fukuoka
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.47,0:08:41.34,Blackboard,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1200,0)}{準決勝}Semi-finals
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:48.66,Sign,,0,0,0,,{禁煙}No smoking
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.77,0:08:46.18,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{や、鮎原くん。おめでとう。}Hey, Ayuhara-kun! Congrats!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.18,0:08:47.28,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{よかった。}Good going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:48.21,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{最高の調子じゃないか。}What a crushing victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.83,0:08:50.69,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{おめでとうなんて未だ早いわよ。}It's still early for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.69,0:08:52.22,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{そうよ、努さん。気が早いわ。}Yeah, Tsutomu-san. Save it for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:54.13,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{や、もう勝ったも同じだよ。}Nope. You've already won.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:56.72,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{今の試合を福岡中の連中も見たけど…}Even though Fukuoka watched your game…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:58.98,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{…皆旬として声もでなかったぜ。}…they were so shocked they haven't said a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.19,0:09:03.33,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{努さんは有頂天に成ってるけづ…}Tsutomu-san's overjoyed, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.33,0:09:05.56,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あたしにはその静かさが恐ろしい。}…that silence is what I fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.04,0:09:07.64,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{素人はいいね。}It must be nice to not know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.64,0:09:13.72,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{あの人達はね、あたしたちの決定XX、研究しにきたのよ。声もでないほど真剣にね。}They came here to learn about our weak points. They were silent because they were focused.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:15.06,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,{キャプテン！}Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.06,0:09:15.83,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{はい。}I'm listening!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.83,0:09:17.46,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,{先生が皆を及んでるわ。}Professor is calling us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.46,0:09:20.28,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,{隣の建物にあるソーホールに来てくれって。}He wants us to go to the next\Nbuilding via the south entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.81,0:09:22.29,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,{話があるんですってよ。}He said he wants to talk to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:22.85,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.85,0:09:25.45,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{作戦会になら、控室でいいじゃないの。}We can discuss strategy here in the waiting room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.45,0:09:28.05,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,{ん、何でかよく分からないけど。}Hmm. I don't understand him very well either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.05,0:09:29.19,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{いいわ。行きましょう。}All right. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:33.00,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{未だ「君はいつからコーチに成ったんだ」なんてやられちゃうもね。}I'm sure we'll hear more\N"when did you become a coach?".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:43.52,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{先生、なんですか？}Professor, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.25,0:09:44.41,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{さ、呼んできました。}You called us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:45.90,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{さ、皆、座った座った。}All right, take a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.26,0:09:48.65,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{これからレコード鑑賞するから、静かに聞くんだぞ。}We'll be listening to a record now, so stay quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:50.03,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{な、何ですって？}Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:53.35,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{あたしたちは東京までレコードを聞きに来たんじゃありません。}We didn't come all the way to Tokyo to listen to music.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.64,0:09:55.23,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{—ね？\N—そうよ。}– Right?\N– Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.78,0:09:58.07,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{一体なんの真似ですか？}Why are we doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.90,0:09:59.75,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{おい、おい。}Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.75,0:10:01.58,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{そんなに大きな声を出さんでも…}Don't be so loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:03.89,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{ここはXXXすぎるんだ。}This room has perfect acoustics.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.89,0:10:05.47,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{聞こえるよ、ちゃんと。}I can hear you very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.47,0:10:06.47,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{この曲はだな。}It's this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.47,0:10:07.85,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{じょ—冗談じゃないわ。}Do-Don't joke around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:09.32,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{あたし試合を見てくる。}I'm going to see the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.32,0:10:10.13,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{—行こう。\N—行こう。}– Let's go.\N– Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:10.84,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{待て。}Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.62,0:10:15.92,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{僕の言うこと聞くんだ。}Listen to what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:20.22,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{僕のやることが例え、君たちに理解できなくても、勝ってものは許さん。}Even if you don't understand what I'm doing,\NI won't allow doing as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.58,0:10:21.63,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{酷いわ。}That's cruel
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.63,0:10:22.72,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{酷すぎるわ。}That's just awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:23.66,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{封建的だわ。}Look, a feudal lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:24.76,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{丸で暴君。}What a tyrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:25.80,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{そうよ。}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:27.54,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{先生、どうかしているんです。}Something's wrong with professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:28.85,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{何も聞いてくれないじゃないの。}I won't listen to anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.17,0:10:30.67,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{何とでも言うないい。}Say what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.67,0:10:31.93,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{だが、これだけ言っておこう。}I will say just this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:35.12,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{福岡中は明法を破り、必ず君たちとあたる。}Fukuoka will surely defeat Meihou and play against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.47,0:10:39.45,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{そして、この福岡中の強さはいくら君たちが試合を見ても、分からない。}And no matter if you watch their games or\hnot, you won't understand their strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:40.88,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{おっしゃり意味が分かりません。}I don't understand what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.88,0:10:42.81,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{いくら考えても分かんないわ。}I don't get it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.81,0:10:43.89,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{そうよ。}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.89,0:10:46.28,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{試合を見ればちゃんと分かるのにさ。}We'll surely understand them when we see their game.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.59,0:10:47.62,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{分からないんだ。}You won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:49.96,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{君たちが見ても分かるわけがないのは当たり前だ。}There's no way you'd get it from mere watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.45,0:10:51.62,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{なぜですか。}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.62,0:10:53.75,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{あたしは先生のおっしゃることが信じられません。}I don't buy it, professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.26,0:10:55.59,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{信じてもらうX困る。}You're giving me a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:56.79,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{じゃ。}How's this:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.79,0:10:58.80,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{なぜ福岡中は強いか、教えよ。}Tell me, why is Fukuoka so strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.99,0:11:04.61,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{それは相手のチームは強ければ強いほど、相手チームの方から負けてしまう。}The stronger your opponent's team is,\Nthe easier their victories are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:09.13,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{ようするに、相手チームが実力を発揮できないようにしてしまう。}In other words, the fewer opportunities for them to demonstrate their true power.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.13,0:11:10.85,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{これが福岡中の(XXX・正体)なのだ。}That is Fukuoka's strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.70,0:11:12.75,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{ヘ？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:13.49,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{そう。}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.49,0:11:16.36,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{だから相手の福岡中を研究してもダメなんだ。}That's why it's no use trying to research them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.10,0:11:18.24,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{問題は君たちだ。}The problem is with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.56,0:11:19.58,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{君たちの自信だ。}Your confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.58,0:11:21.58,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{試合中いかに実力を出せるか。}How proficient can you get in the match?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.06,0:11:23.07,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{それだけだ。}That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.07,0:11:24.26,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{それだけしかない。}That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.65,0:11:26.63,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{じゃ、どうすれば、どんな作戦が？}Then what do we do? What's our strategy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:31.23,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{福岡中との試合に勝てるとすれば、どんなことになっても、自信。}The most important in playing against Fukuoka is to believe in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:33.50,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{自分達の力を信用して疑らないこと。}Do not doubt your own strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:35.09,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{作戦じゃない。}It's not the strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.14,0:11:38.42,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{言ってみれば、作戦なき作戦。}If I had to name it, it's a "strategy without strategy".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:40.15,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{作戦なき作戦…}A "strategy without strategy".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.62,0:11:41.41,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{そう。}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.41,0:11:42.30,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{それしかないのだ。}That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:44.07,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{ここにできるのはこれまで。}That is what we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.33,0:11:47.33,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{後は福岡中に負けない、君たちの専心力は便りだ。}What's left is not to lose your confidence before Fukuoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:50.27,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{あの、それじゃ、当たって砕けろってことですか？}So nothing ventured, nothing gained?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.71,0:11:51.14,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{うん。}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:53.50,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{作戦も考えること無駄ということ。}Thinking of a strategy is a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.32,0:11:56.75,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{相手のペースにXXX、マイペース。}We need to impose our pace on the opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:11:58.43,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{冷静にいつものようにある。}We should stay calm and play as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.43,0:11:59.69,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{そうですね、先生？}Is that right, professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.51,0:12:01.39,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{そうだ。}Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.39,0:12:04.77,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{簡単なことなのに、一番難しいことのように思えてきたわ。}Easier said than done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.59,0:12:07.15,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{さ、レコードを聞こう。}All right, let's play it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.15,0:12:08.30,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{未だ時間がある。}We still have the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.96,0:12:09.88,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{—はい。\N—ぁあい。}– Yes.\N– Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.86,0:12:15.22,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{こいつは、誰でも知っている、有名なベートーベンの第五番運命だ。}It's something everyone knows: Beethoven's Symphony No. 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.65,0:12:17.54,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{専心できない余裕を作り出すんだな。}It helps find a way those who have lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:33.56,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{作戦なき作戦しか打つ手がないなんて。}Nothing can be done except\Nthe "strategy without strategy"…?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:35.76,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{考えもうつかないXXXだわ。}I guess it's no use dwelling on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.36,0:12:50.11,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:17.15,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:21.15,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.75,0:13:25.63,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{はああい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.09,0:13:30.20,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{バレー会の名門明法学園XXX。}Meihou, the volleyball queen, is in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:32.21,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{すでに、大一セットはあっという間に取られ。}They've already lost the first set.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.21,0:13:35.37,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{第二セットも調子の出ないまま、福岡中のペースでゲームXX。}They haven't recovered in this set\Nand Fukuoka keeps the lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:36.72,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{すでに、１３対９。}It's 13 to 9 already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.72,0:13:40.25,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{今又かきのうちのライン擦れ擦れの強くもないスパイクが決まっておきます。}Again, Kakinouchi's has landed another spike just grazing the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:42.00,Blackboard,,0,0,0,,{福岡中・明法学園}Fukuoka ・ Meihou
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:43.89,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{１４対９となりました。いよいよマッチポイントに成りました、福岡中。}It's now 14 to 9. Finally, the match point goes to Fukuoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.89,0:13:46.05,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{この試合は全く明法らしくありません。}This match is completely unlike Meihou.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:47.37,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{どうでしょう、山口さん。}Back to you, Yamaguchi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.66,0:13:50.04,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{実力の半分も出てない感じですね。}It's not even a half of the energy I expected to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.04,0:13:52.42,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{恐ろしい、実に恐ろしい。}I'm really surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.42,0:13:57.41,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{福岡中のようなチームのXXXなバレー会にとって良いことか悪いことか分かりませんが…}I don't know if it's a good or a bad thing for a team such as Fukuoka…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.41,0:14:00.65,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{…前後ろ一度相手に回ってチームはしっかりペースを乱され…}…but at any rate, they managed to\hgreatly shake their enemy's team…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:03.49,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{…二度と立ち直れないほどショック与えられてしまうそうです。}…and deal shock that might be never recovered from.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.49,0:14:05.30,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{ほ？どうしてXXそんなことが？}Oh? What makes you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:09.63,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{え、さっき前回の優勝チーム、岩井中のXXコーチ相見られまして…}Err, I approached the coach of last year's winners, Iwai Middle School.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.63,0:14:11.53,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{こう言ってましたな。}And he said this:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.94,0:14:14.85,Default,Iwai's coach,0,0,0,,{や、面目ない、予選で降られましてね。}I'm ashamed we were defeated in the qualifiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.85,0:14:18.04,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{その福岡中すこし聞きたいね。}Hm. I'd like to ask you about that Fukuoka Middle School.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:21.85,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{内緒変わった強さを持ったチームなので解説の仕様は無くてね。}For such a strong team I have very little commentary on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.85,0:14:24.85,Default,Iwai's coach,0,0,0,,{なにがXXXにはXXX話ですが、}It's a bad story.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.85,0:14:31.21,Default,Iwai's coach,0,0,0,,{家の、つまり岩井中では主将は初め、試合に出たレギュラーは全部バレーボールを辞めると言い出しましてね。}Every one of our Iwai's club regular players said they want to quit volleyball after that match.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.21,0:14:32.19,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{お？}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.19,0:14:36.45,Default,Iwai's coach,0,0,0,,{その理由は酷いもので、詰まらなくなった。}They said they've lost interest in it.\N{自信がも出ません。}They lost their confidence too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:39.62,Default,Iwai's coach,0,0,0,,{と言うだけで、腑抜けXXになってしまっているんですよ。}That said, I think it's absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.85,0:14:42.53,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{ほ？}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:45.35,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{なにが聞いている私もXXXがあるような話ですね。}It's a curious story.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:50.69,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{だから、きっと明法学園のよしむらいかも、あんなに調子を狂わせられてXXだと思いますね。}This is why I think Meihou Academy and Yoshimura's team might turn out similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.79,0:14:54.34,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.03,0:14:55.80,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.18,0:14:57.73,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{XXX、お願い！}Chinko, it's yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.73,0:14:59.53,Default,Yoshimura,0,0,0,,{XXXダメだよ！手を!}Don't hit it! It's out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.00,0:15:30.95,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{山口さん。}Yamaguchi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:33.62,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{今のは完全にラインX出てしまったXですね。}The last spike would be an out, wouldn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:34.77,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{そうです。}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.77,0:15:38.53,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{もうやっている戦士のちょっとした精神錯乱に落ちってXでしょう。}Looks like the players' mental\hcomposure is in pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.03,0:15:43.46,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{なまじっか名宝は実績に高いXXXラリーに続いてしまって言うが、}Meihou might have a history of achievements, but today…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:49.18,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{あ、私もXXXよしむらたちをこれ以上戦わせたくないような気がしてきました。}…I feel like I do not want to see Yoshimura-san struggle any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.00,0:15:51.93,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:53.30,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:55.42,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{はいっす！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:15:57.13,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{はぁい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.63,0:15:58.59,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:24.62,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:26.85,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{お！XXX！XXX！}Oh! It went through!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.85,0:16:30.52,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{まったく外れているボールを(XXX・びっしりXXX選手)明法学園がXXX。}Meihou players' receive a ball that was completely out of the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.52,0:16:33.37,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{何かもまともな精神状態とはないようであります。}The players seem extremely confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.84,0:16:38.59,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.45,0:16:41.05,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.76,0:16:44.35,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{出てる！大アウト！}It's out again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:45.19,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{あ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:03.45,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{いよいよ六回めのマッチポイント。サーブな打たれます。}At last, the sixth match point. The server hits the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.45,0:17:04.88,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{—それ！\N—それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.88,0:17:06.84,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{よし。とどめXXX。}All right, let's finish this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.58,0:17:09.29,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.64,0:17:10.52,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.75,0:17:15.06,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{見事な(XXX・ショックを・速度)！}Splendid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.06,0:17:19.30,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{ついに福岡中の勝利。名門明法学園完敗いたしました。}Finally, Fukuoka Middle School wins. The prestigious Meihou Academy is defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.69,0:17:21.99,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{さすが明法XXX}As expected from Meihou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:24.36,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{岩井中以来の強敵だったよ。}They were the strongest since Iwai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.96,0:17:26.66,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{いよいよ決戦じゃ富士見学園対。}At last, the final with Fujimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:28.92,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{鮎原・早川コンビも。}And the Ayuhara-Hayakawa duo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.92,0:17:32.31,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{あのよしむらさんと同じ目に合わせこっつなる。フフ。}Let's put them through the same as Yoshimura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.63,0:17:39.32,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{ただいま明法学園のキャプテンよしむら選手が(XX・熱戦)のため意識を失い…}The captain Yoshimura of Meihou Academy, due to the fierce match, has lost consciousness…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:41.69,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{医師の診察を受けております。}…and is under medical care right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.69,0:17:46.33,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{未だ次の決勝戦は福岡中学と富士見学園との間で、}The next game between Fukuoka Middle School and Fujimi Academy…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.33,0:17:48.66,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{三十分後に開始されます。}…will commence in 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.66,0:17:52.11,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{両チームとも十分前にはコートに集まっていただきます。}Both teams are to gather on the court 10 minutes before the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.69,0:17:56.93,Default,Yoshimura,0,0,0,,{辞める…}I quit…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:58.77,Default,Yoshimura,0,0,0,,{バレー…辞める。}I'm quitting volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.08,0:18:01.60,Default,Yoshimura,0,0,0,,{何をやってもだ。}No matter what happens…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.67,0:18:07.84,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{富士見学園は今の試合を見てなかったようですね。}Looks like Fujimi Academy didn't watch the previous match.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.84,0:18:08.95,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{え。そうなんです。}That is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.95,0:18:11.75,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{こちらに情報が入ってるんですが、それにXます人ですね。}We got an information I'll\hbe\hrelaying to our listeners.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.75,0:18:15.26,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{全員は試合が始まると隣の(X・小ホール)でミーティングを初め、}When the game started, all Fujimi members gathered in a building next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.26,0:18:17.49,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{今だ扉を締め切って出てこないそうですね。}They shut the doors and didn't step out thus far.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.18,0:18:19.00,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{ほ、ホール？}A building?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.50,0:18:20.32,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{なんですか、それは？}Where exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.96,0:18:22.89,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{たしか、鑑賞質とか。}I think it's an auditorium.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:24.66,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{な、何ですって？}S-Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:28.62,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{本当に何だってそんな所で閉じこもってるんですかね。}One can't help but wonder why they shut themselves in such a room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:32.04,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{相手を少しでも(X・しゅりょう)に、試合を見ると言うなら分かりますかね、山口さん。}I'd understand if they came to research the game. Right, Yamaguchi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.64,0:18:34.36,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{もしや棄権するなどと言う。}Maybe they're abstaining from the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.36,0:18:36.23,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{や、そんなことはない。}N-Nah, it can't be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.23,0:18:39.65,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{XX福岡中攻略のポイントはそこにあるのか。}Maybe there is another point to their actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.65,0:18:40.17,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:42.13,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{え、ええや。}Ah, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.12,0:18:44.56,Default,Commentator 2,0,0,0,,{はっきりとは。}Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.61,0:18:53.48,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{君たちは自信を失う時、それは敗北だ。}When you lose confidence, it's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:55.46,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,{このまま福岡中に打つかっていくんだ。}We need to take Fukuoka head-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:18:56.17,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:18:56.82,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,{はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:18:57.82,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{も一本！}One more!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:18:58.69,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,{はい、はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.21,0:19:03.13,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{張り切ってきましょう！}Let's keep the high spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.76,0:19:07.16,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{こずえ、頑張ってね。}Kozue, good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:11.62,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{パパもいてくれれば心強いのに、とても一人で見ていられないわ。}I wish papa, who is of a stronger heart,\Nwould watch it with me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:13.81,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:14.86,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{そら！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.11,0:19:16.15,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{ほら！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.98,0:19:18.89,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{試合会誌五分前。}Five minutes until the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.36,0:19:23.02,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{両チームXXXコートの外に出てください。}Both teams are to step off the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.11,0:19:24.93,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{練習ストップ。}Practice stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.40,0:19:27.40,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{なにするの？}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.73,0:19:29.56,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{あら、(XX・立った)のね。ごめんね。}Oh, I'm sorry it hit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:32.31,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{XXX鮎原さん。}It wasn't on purpose, Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:33.89,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{何ですって？}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.34,0:19:36.31,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{あら？喧嘩をうるき？}Oh? Wanna fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.31,0:19:37.08,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{ちょっと！}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.08,0:19:37.61,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{なかざわ！}Nakazawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:39.45,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{いい加減にしろ、君たち！}Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.52,0:19:44.52,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{そうだ。}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.52,0:19:46.45,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{この手に乗らないことが大切なんだわ。}It's important not to get taken in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:03.87,Default,Referee,0,0,0,,{キャプテンは先行決めてください。}Both captains, choose who serves first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.91,0:20:07.28,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{じゃん、けん！}Rock, paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:13.28,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{じゃんけん！}Rock paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.01,0:20:20.71,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{どういうつもりか知らないけど、その手に乗らないわ。}I don't know what you're scheming, but it won't work on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:23.71,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{やってん、どうせあたしの勝ち(X・たい・だ)。}Whatever. It's our win anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.71,0:20:25.05,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{じゃん、けん、ぽん！}Rock, paper, scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.51,0:20:28.03,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{フフ。}Fufu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:30.19,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{なにか嫌をかんがする。}I have a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.56,0:20:36.18,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{いよいよ春の全国中学女子バレーボール選手権でありもクライマックスを向かえようとしております。}At last, spring All-Japan Middle School Women's Volleyball Championships are reaching climax.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.18,0:20:38.65,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{良好とも試合前から激しい火花を散らす。}Both teams are in high spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:40.71,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{XXX}We're about to see a splendid match.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:44.26,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{福岡のキャプテンかきのうちはご存知の回転レシーブの名レシーバ。}Fukuoka's captain Kakinouchi is\hfamous for her revolving receive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:47.73,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{いっぽ、富士見のキャプテン鮎原は左右両手の名アタッカー。}Meanwhile, Fujimi's captain Ayuhara is known as an ambidextrous attacker.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:50.33,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{アタッカー対レシーバ—面白い対決であります。}It's an interesting fight between an attacker and a receiver.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:52.67,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{果たして勝利はどちらのものになりましょうか？}Which one will emerge victorious?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.87,0:20:57.17,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.41,0:21:01.35,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{さ、来い！}Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:03.12,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{行くわよ、かきのうちさん。}Here we go, Kakinouchi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.97,0:21:08.74,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:09.97,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.97,0:21:10.35,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.96,0:21:11.58,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:12.17,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.17,0:21:12.69,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{あ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.17,0:21:15.71,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:18.46,Sign,,0,0,0,,{ガンバレ富士見学園}Good luck Fujimi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.05,0:21:18.03,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,{頑張ってね！}Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.03,0:21:19.61,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{—しっかり、富士見！\N—頑張れよ！}– Godspeed, Fujimi!\N– Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:22.26,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{すごい。ラインを狙って打つX神業だわ。}Amazing. Her aim at line is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:26.25,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.17,0:21:30.76,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{アタック！}Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.06,0:21:31.64,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:32.30,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.09,0:21:33.81,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.90,0:21:36.56,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{そぉれ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.98,0:21:39.55,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{鮎原さん、フェイントよ！}Ayuhara-san, let's try feinting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.30,0:21:40.94,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.68,0:21:43.00,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.76,0:21:46.10,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{しまった！XXX皆にダメにされてしまうわ。}Damn! I can't penetrate it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.59,0:21:47.24,Blackboard,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,50,255,0,1500,2500,3550)}{富士見中・福岡中}Fujimi ・ Fukuoka
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.10,0:21:46.83,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{どうしよう？}What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.72,0:21:50.57,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{どうやらこの試合も福岡中のペースに成ってきたようです。}Looks like Fukuoka completely controls this match as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.06,0:21:53.70,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{あ、どうやら、富士見にサーブ権のもらったようです。}Oh, Fujimi got a serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:56.19,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{サーバーはキャプテンの鮎原こずえであります。}Server will be captain Ayuhara Kozue.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.84,0:21:58.76,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{「木の葉落とし」で得点を稼げなくちゃ。}I guess I have to use "Leaf Fall".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.50,0:22:04.15,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.52,0:22:10.84,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{すごいファイト！}Excellent receive!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.84,0:22:12.47,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{さすがレシーブのにかきのうち。}As expected from Kakinouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.47,0:22:15.01,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{見事に評判の「木の葉落とし」を拾い上げました。}She perfectly warded off the famous "Leaf Fall".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.37,0:22:16.90,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.08,0:22:18.60,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.41,0:22:21.71,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{あゆはら、何をしても、無駄だ。}Ayuhara-san. Your struggle is futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.98,0:22:26.59,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.02,0:22:27.69,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.11,0:22:32.90,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{第一セット福岡中は取りました。}Fukuoka wins the first set.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.14,0:22:28.79,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.24,0:22:32.37,Sign,,0,0,0,,{ガンバレ福岡中学}Good luck, Fukuoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:34.37,Blackboard,,0,0,0,,{福岡中・富士見中}Fukuoka ・ Fujimi
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.46,0:22:35.56,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{分かっただろう？}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.56,0:22:36.94,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{福岡中の怖さが。}This is Fukuoka's strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.44,0:22:40.33,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{コートの中で戦ってみて、初めて分かる怖さだ。}It's something you can only see by yourself in the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.25,0:22:45.10,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{試合を見ているだけでは、本当に分かれにはしない。}There's no way to learn it just from watching the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.62,0:22:50.05,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{さ、本当の試合はこれからだ。}All right. The real match begins now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.05,0:22:52.88,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{お前たちのバレーをしろ。それだけだ。行け！}Do your thing. That is all. Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.88,0:22:53.71,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{—はい！\N—はい！}– Yes sir!\N– Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.72,0:22:56.31,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{第二セット開始であります。}The second set begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.31,0:22:58.23,Default,Commentator 1,0,0,0,,{両チームそれぞれポジションにつきました。}Each team assumed positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.79,0:23:03.90,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{ただいま関東代表、明法学園はキャプテンのよしむら選手を初め四人の戦士は…}The Kantou's representative, Meihou Academy, due to captain Yoshimura's and four players'…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.90,0:23:08.80,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{…さきほどの福岡中学との試合で不調したため三位決定戦も棄権しました。}…worsening state from the match with Fukuoka, will abstain from the third place play-off.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.80,0:23:09.37,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.37,0:23:13.97,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{したがって三位は北海道代表、札幌中学に決まりました。}Therefore the third place goes by walkover to the Hokkaidou's representative, Sapporo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.44,0:23:16.17,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{よしむらさん不調しちゃって？}Yoshimura-san's state worsened?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.17,0:23:17.68,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{一体どういうことなの？}What did they mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.23,0:23:22.13,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{かきのうちさん、よしむらさんたちになにがあったの？}Kakinouchi-san. What happened to Yoshimura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.78,0:23:23.84,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{ハハハハ。}Hahahaha.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.84,0:23:25.75,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{別にあたしのせじゃないよ。}It's not like we did anything to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.75,0:23:28.25,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{それに、不調言うても精神的だもんよ。}Plus I think they referred to the mental state.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.25,0:23:28.89,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{ま。}Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.64,0:23:31.69,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{勝手に気が狂ってしまった。}She went crazy on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.98,0:23:36.36,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{あんたたちもXXXとはかぎらない。}I can't be held responsible\Nif you end up that way as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.36,0:23:37.40,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{ハハハハ。}Hahahaha.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.84,0:23:38.25,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{え？}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.17,0:23:40.73,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{勝手に気が狂った？}Went crazy on her own?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.81,0:23:58.06,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{福岡中XXXワンセットを落とした富士見学園。}Fukuoka wins the first match against Fujimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.06,0:23:59.71,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{さっきの音楽を思い出せ。}"Remember the music."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.71,0:24:04.10,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{と言う本郷コーチの言葉で立ち直ったこずえたちは第二セットを取る。}—says coach Hongou. Kozue, keeping these words in mind, wins the second set.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.10,0:24:06.06,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{ついに、決勝の第三セット。}Finally, the decisive set.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.06,0:24:08.80,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{だが、福岡中学のXXX攻撃に…}Fukuoka starts with a fierce attack…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.80,0:24:11.85,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{…富士見学園は十五対十四ピンチを向かえる。}…and Fujimi Academy faces a\hpinch with the score of 15 to 14.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.85,0:24:17.30,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{そんな時、相手のXXXこずえは素晴らしい作戦を思いついた。}Just then, Kozue, who reclaimed the\hright to serve, has a wonderful idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.30,0:24:20.89,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{さ、来週のアタックナンバーワンをお楽しみに。}Please look forward to the next episode.
